<h3 data-start=3D"2220" data-end=3D"2241"><code data-start=3D"2224" data-en=
d=3D"2241">vibestack apply</code></h3>
<ul data-start=3D"2242" data-end=3D"2329">
<li data-start=3D"2242" data-end=3D"2284">
<p data-start=3D"2244" data-end=3D"2284">applies hunks into commits (new co=
mmits)</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"2285" data-end=3D"2329">
<p data-start=3D"2287" data-end=3D"2329">creates branches <code data-start=
=3D"2304" data-end=3D"2314">stack/01</code>, <code data-start=3D"2316" data=
-end=3D"2326">stack/02</code>, =E2=80=A6</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start=3D"2331" data-end=3D"2353"><code data-start=3D"2335" data-en=
d=3D"2353">vibestack verify</code></h3>
<ul data-start=3D"2354" data-end=3D"2606">
<li data-start=3D"2354" data-end=3D"2606">
<p data-start=3D"2356" data-end=3D"2381">for each commit in order:</p>
<ul data-start=3D"2384" data-end=3D"2606">
<li data-start=3D"2384" data-end=3D"2406">
<p data-start=3D"2386" data-end=3D"2406">checkout that commit</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"2409" data-end=3D"2480">
<p data-start=3D"2411" data-end=3D"2480">run local CI equivalent commands (=
or <code data-start=3D"2448" data-end=3D"2453">act</code>/similar if you wa=
nt later)</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"2483" data-end=3D"2606">
<p data-start=3D"2485" data-end=3D"2494">if fails:</p>
<ul data-start=3D"2499" data-end=3D"2606">
<li data-start=3D"2499" data-end=3D"2538">
<p data-start=3D"2501" data-end=3D"2538">auto-merge with next commit and re=
try</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"2543" data-end=3D"2606">
