<li data-start=3D"2629" data-end=3D"2765">
<p data-start=3D"2631" data-end=3D"2651">opens PRs on GitHub:</p>
<ul data-start=3D"2654" data-end=3D"2765">
<li data-start=3D"2654" data-end=3D"2679">
<p data-start=3D"2656" data-end=3D"2679">PR1 ready, PR2..n draft</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"2682" data-end=3D"2765">
<p data-start=3D"2684" data-end=3D"2765">PR bodies include: dependency, tes=
t commands, and =E2=80=9Cthis PR is CI-green by itself=E2=80=9D</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start=3D"2767" data-end=3D"2787"><code data-start=3D"2771" data-en=
d=3D"2787">vibestack sync</code></h3>
