<li data-start=3D"3455" data-end=3D"3545">
<p data-start=3D"3457" data-end=3D"3545">=E2=80=9Crefactor PR=E2=80=9D + =
=E2=80=9Cfeature PR=E2=80=9D as separate if it risks CI failures or review =
denial ripple</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"3546" data-end=3D"3623">
<p data-start=3D"3548" data-end=3D"3623">splitting inside the same function=
 unless necessary (causes semantic drift)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 data-start=3D"3625" data-end=3D"3665">The =E2=80=9CAI agent=E2=80=9D pa=
rt you probably mean</h2>
<p data-start=3D"3666" data-end=3D"3730">You want more than heuristics. So =
do a <strong data-start=3D"3705" data-end=3D"3729">two-phase agent loop</st=
rong>:</p>
<ol data-start=3D"3732" data-end=3D"3752">
<li data-start=3D"3732" data-end=3D"3752">
<p data-start=3D"3735" data-end=3D"3752"><strong data-start=3D"3735" data-e=
nd=3D"3752">Planner agent</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<ul data-start=3D"3753" data-end=3D"3776">
<li data-start=3D"3753" data-end=3D"3776">
<p data-start=3D"3755" data-end=3D"3776">outputs the JSON plan</p>
</li>
</ul>
<ol start=3D"2" data-start=3D"3778" data-end=3D"3799">
<li data-start=3D"3778" data-end=3D"3799">
<p data-start=3D"3781" data-end=3D"3799"><strong data-start=3D"3781" data-e=
nd=3D"3799">Validator loop</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<ul data-start=3D"3800" data-end=3D"3986">
<li data-start=3D"3800" data-end=3D"3845">
<p data-start=3D"3802" data-end=3D"3845">tool applies PR1..n locally and ru=
ns checks</p>
