</li>
<li data-start=3D"3930" data-end=3D"3986">
<p data-start=3D"3932" data-end=3D"3986">agent revises plan (usually merges=
 PRs or moves hunks)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start=3D"3988" data-end=3D"4052">This is how you avoid hand-wavy =
