</li>
<li data-start=3D"96" data-end=3D"143">
<p data-start=3D"98" data-end=3D"143"><strong data-start=3D"98" data-end=3D=
"143">CLI runs a representative CI lane locally</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"144" data-end=3D"203">
<p data-start=3D"146" data-end=3D"203">If anything fails: <strong data-star=
t=3D"165" data-end=3D"203">auto-merge adjacent slices + retry</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"204" data-end=3D"268">
<p data-start=3D"206" data-end=3D"268">Then push a <strong data-start=3D"21=
8" data-end=3D"241">linear stack of PRs</strong>: top =3D ready, rest =3D d=
raft</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"269" data-end=3D"377">
<p data-start=3D"271" data-end=3D"377">If CI fails on GitHub later or you a=
djust PR1 from review: <strong data-start=3D"330" data-end=3D"355">force-pu=
sh downstream</strong> to keep history clean</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 data-start=3D"379" data-end=3D"390">MVP flow</h2>
<h3 data-start=3D"392" data-end=3D"412">0) Preconditions</h3>
<ul data-start=3D"413" data-end=3D"541">
<li data-start=3D"413" data-end=3D"492">
<p data-start=3D"415" data-end=3D"492">Repo uses <strong data-start=3D"425"=
 data-end=3D"443">GitHub Actions</strong> and has runnable steps locally mo=
st of the time.</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"493" data-end=3D"541">
<p data-start=3D"495" data-end=3D"541">You=E2=80=99re okay with force-push =
on stack branches.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start=3D"543" data-end=3D"567">1) <code data-start=3D"550" data-en=
d=3D"567">vibestack split</code></h3>
<p data-start=3D"568" data-end=3D"578"><strong data-start=3D"568" data-end=
=3D"578">Inputs</strong></p>
<ul data-start=3D"579" data-end=3D"677">
<li data-start=3D"579" data-end=3D"616">
<p data-start=3D"581" data-end=3D"616">current branch (your big vibe diff)<=
/p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"617" data-end=3D"677">
<p data-start=3D"619" data-end=3D"677">optional chat transcript (only for P=
R titles/descriptions)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start=3D"679" data-end=3D"690"><strong data-start=3D"679" data-end=
=3D"690">Outputs</strong></p>
<ul data-start=3D"691" data-end=3D"736">
<li data-start=3D"691" data-end=3D"736">
<p data-start=3D"693" data-end=3D"736"><code data-start=3D"693" data-end=3D=
"710">stack.plan.json</code> (machine-applicable plan)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start=3D"738" data-end=3D"763">Plan structure (minimum):</p>
<ul data-start=3D"764" data-end=3D"847">
<li data-start=3D"764" data-end=3D"782">
<p data-start=3D"766" data-end=3D"782">PR list in order</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"783" data-end=3D"847">
<p data-start=3D"785" data-end=3D"847">for each PR: selected files + (optio=
nally) hunk ranges + title</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start=3D"849" data-end=3D"873">2) <code data-start=3D"856" data-en=
d=3D"873">vibestack apply</code></h3>
<ul data-start=3D"874" data-end=3D"1031">
<li data-start=3D"874" data-end=3D"964">
<p data-start=3D"876" data-end=3D"964">Creates <strong data-start=3D"884" d=
ata-end=3D"899">new commits</strong> from scratch according to the plan (do=
n=E2=80=99t preserve old commits).</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"965" data-end=3D"1031">
<p data-start=3D"967" data-end=3D"990">Creates local branches:</p>
<ul data-start=3D"993" data-end=3D"1031">
<li data-start=3D"993" data-end=3D"1031">
<p data-start=3D"995" data-end=3D"1031"><code data-start=3D"995" data-end=
=3D"1009">stack/01-...</code>, <code data-start=3D"1011" data-end=3D"1025">=
stack/02-...</code>, etc.</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start=3D"1033" data-end=3D"1058">3) <code data-start=3D"1040" data=
-end=3D"1058">vibestack verify</code></h3>
<ul data-start=3D"1059" data-end=3D"1287">
<li data-start=3D"1059" data-end=3D"1093">
<p data-start=3D"1061" data-end=3D"1093">Parses <code data-start=3D"1068" d=
ata-end=3D"1093">.github/workflows/*.yml</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"1094" data-end=3D"1214">
<p data-start=3D"1096" data-end=3D"1130">Chooses a <strong data-start=3D"11=
06" data-end=3D"1129">representative lane</strong>:</p>
<ul data-start=3D"1133" data-end=3D"1214">
<li data-start=3D"1133" data-end=3D"1150">
<p data-start=3D"1135" data-end=3D"1150"><code data-start=3D"1135" data-end=
=3D"1150">ubuntu-latest</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"1153" data-end=3D"1214">
<p data-start=3D"1155" data-end=3D"1214">highest stable language version in=
 matrix (or repo default)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"1215" data-end=3D"1258">
<p data-start=3D"1217" data-end=3D"1258">Extracts runnable commands when po=
ssible.</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"1259" data-end=3D"1287">
<p data-start=3D"1261" data-end=3D"1287">Runs them per PR boundary.</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start=3D"1289" data-end=3D"1311">If PR k fails locally:</p>
<ul data-start=3D"1312" data-end=3D"1448">
<li data-start=3D"1312" data-end=3D"1371">
<p data-start=3D"1314" data-end=3D"1371">automatically <strong data-start=
=3D"1328" data-end=3D"1351">merge PR k + PR k+1</strong> (collapse boundary=
)</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"1372" data-end=3D"1393">
<p data-start=3D"1374" data-end=3D"1393">re-run verification</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"1394" data-end=3D"1448">
<p data-start=3D"1396" data-end=3D"1448">repeat until either green or stack=
 collapses to 1 PR</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start=3D"1450" data-end=3D"1517">This is how you satisfy =E2=80=9Ce=
verything must pass CI=E2=80=9D without guessing.</p>
<h3 data-start=3D"1519" data-end=3D"1542">4) <code data-start=3D"1526" data=
-end=3D"1542">vibestack push</code></h3>
<ul data-start=3D"1543" data-end=3D"1812">
<li data-start=3D"1543" data-end=3D"1566">
<p data-start=3D"1545" data-end=3D"1566">Pushes stack branches</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"1567" data-end=3D"1660">
<p data-start=3D"1569" data-end=3D"1619">Opens PRs on <span class=3D"hover:=
entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span =
class=3D"whitespace-normal">GitHub</span></span></p>
<ul data-start=3D"1622" data-end=3D"1660">
<li data-start=3D"1622" data-end=3D"1638">
<p data-start=3D"1624" data-end=3D"1638">PR1: <strong data-start=3D"1629" d=
ata-end=3D"1638">Ready</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"1641" data-end=3D"1660">
<p data-start=3D"1643" data-end=3D"1660">PR2..n: <strong data-start=3D"1651=
" data-end=3D"1660">Draft</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"1661" data-end=3D"1812">
<p data-start=3D"1663" data-end=3D"1685">Each PR body includes:</p>
<ul data-start=3D"1688" data-end=3D"1812">
<li data-start=3D"1688" data-end=3D"1720">
<p data-start=3D"1690" data-end=3D"1720">depends-on link to previous PR</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"1723" data-end=3D"1769">
<p data-start=3D"1725" data-end=3D"1769">=E2=80=9CRepresentative lane local=
ly: &lt;what we ran&gt;=E2=80=9D</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"1772" data-end=3D"1812">
<p data-start=3D"1774" data-end=3D"1812">=E2=80=9CAll lanes enforced on Git=
Hub Actions=E2=80=9D</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-start=3D"1814" data-end=3D"1865">5) <code data-start=3D"1821" data=
-end=3D"1837">vibestack sync</code> (after review edits on PR1)</h3>
<ul data-start=3D"1866" data-end=3D"2034">
<li data-start=3D"1866" data-end=3D"1899">
<p data-start=3D"1868" data-end=3D"1899">Rebases PR2..n onto updated PR1</p=
>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"1900" data-end=3D"1942">
