<h3 data-start=3D"2036" data-end=3D"2077">6) <code data-start=3D"2043" data=
-end=3D"2059">vibestack next</code> (after PR1 merge)</h3>
<ul data-start=3D"2078" data-end=3D"2156">
<li data-start=3D"2078" data-end=3D"2105">
<p data-start=3D"2080" data-end=3D"2105">Rebases stack onto <code data-star=
t=3D"2099" data-end=3D"2105">main</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"2106" data-end=3D"2134">
<p data-start=3D"2108" data-end=3D"2134">Converts PR2 draft =E2=86=92 ready=
</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"2135" data-end=3D"2156">
<p data-start=3D"2137" data-end=3D"2156">Leaves PR3..n draft</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start=3D"2158" data-end=3D"2161">
<h2 data-start=3D"2163" data-end=3D"2218">The AI agent: what it must produc=
e (or it=E2=80=99s useless)</h2>
<p data-start=3D"2219" data-end=3D"2302">You need the agent to output <stro=
ng data-start=3D"2248" data-end=3D"2290">a plan you can apply deterministic=
ally</strong>, not vibes.</p>
<h3 data-start=3D"2304" data-end=3D"2342">What the agent should optimize fo=
r</h3>
<ol data-start=3D"2343" data-end=3D"2461">
<li data-start=3D"2343" data-end=3D"2407">
<p data-start=3D"2346" data-end=3D"2407">Boundaries that are likely to stay=
 green (compile/lint/tests)</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"2408" data-end=3D"2440">
<p data-start=3D"2411" data-end=3D"2440">Minimal cross-PR dependencies</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"2441" data-end=3D"2461">
<p data-start=3D"2444" data-end=3D"2461">Reviewable slices</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h3 data-start=3D"2463" data-end=3D"2513">Heuristic slicing rules (TS + Pyt=
hon friendly)</h3>
<p data-start=3D"2514" data-end=3D"2566">Buckets (merge/collapse as needed =
to keep CI green):</p>
<ol data-start=3D"2567" data-end=3D"2765">
<li data-start=3D"2567" data-end=3D"2643">
<p data-start=3D"2570" data-end=3D"2643"><strong data-start=3D"2570" data-e=
nd=3D"2594">Additive foundations</strong>: new modules/types/helpers that d=
on=E2=80=99t break lint</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"2644" data-end=3D"2692">
<p data-start=3D"2647" data-end=3D"2692"><strong data-start=3D"2647" data-e=
nd=3D"2664">Core behavior</strong>: logic changes + unit tests</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"2693" data-end=3D"2744">
<p data-start=3D"2696" data-end=3D"2744"><strong data-start=3D"2696" data-e=
nd=3D"2706">Wiring</strong>: routes/DI/config + integration tests</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"2745" data-end=3D"2765">
<p data-start=3D"2748" data-end=3D"2765"><strong data-start=3D"2748" data-e=
nd=3D"2765">Docs/examples</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start=3D"2767" data-end=3D"2773">Rules:</p>
<ul data-start=3D"2774" data-end=3D"3028">
<li data-start=3D"2774" data-end=3D"2833">
<p data-start=3D"2776" data-end=3D"2833">Don=E2=80=99t split within a singl=
e small function unless forced.</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"2834" data-end=3D"2889">
<p data-start=3D"2836" data-end=3D"2889">Keep tests with the behavior they =
validate (default).</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"2890" data-end=3D"3028">
<p data-start=3D"2892" data-end=3D"2942">If TS lint complains about unused =
exports, either:</p>
<ul data-start=3D"2945" data-end=3D"3028">
<li data-start=3D"2945" data-end=3D"2986">
<p data-start=3D"2947" data-end=3D"2986">keep the first usage in the same P=
R, or</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"2989" data-end=3D"3028">
<p data-start=3D"2991" data-end=3D"3028">collapse PRs (don=E2=80=99t add du=
mmy usage).</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start=3D"3030" data-end=3D"3033">
<h2 data-start=3D"3035" data-end=3D"3091">CI inference: how =E2=80=9Crepres=
entative lane locally=E2=80=9D works</h2>
<p data-start=3D"3092" data-end=3D"3127">You parse workflow YAML and answer=
:</p>
<ul data-start=3D"3128" data-end=3D"3196">
<li data-start=3D"3128" data-end=3D"3160">
<p data-start=3D"3130" data-end=3D"3160">which workflows trigger on PRs</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"3161" data-end=3D"3196">
<p data-start=3D"3163" data-end=3D"3196">which job is the =E2=80=9Cmain tes=
t lane=E2=80=9D</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start=3D"3198" data-end=3D"3252">Representative lane selection (sim=
ple and defensible):</p>
<ul data-start=3D"3253" data-end=3D"3520">
<li data-start=3D"3253" data-end=3D"3325">
<p data-start=3D"3255" data-end=3D"3325">pick the first job that runs on <c=
ode data-start=3D"3287" data-end=3D"3301">pull_request</code> and contains =
test steps</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"3326" data-end=3D"3350">
<p data-start=3D"3328" data-end=3D"3350">choose <code data-start=3D"3335" d=
ata-end=3D"3350">ubuntu-latest</code></p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"3351" data-end=3D"3520">
<p data-start=3D"3353" data-end=3D"3381">pick one matrix combination:</p>
<ul data-start=3D"3384" data-end=3D"3520">
<li data-start=3D"3384" data-end=3D"3453">
<p data-start=3D"3386" data-end=3D"3453">Node: repo=E2=80=99s <code data-st=
art=3D"3399" data-end=3D"3407">.nvmrc</code> / <code data-start=3D"3410" da=
ta-end=3D"3424">engines.node</code> / otherwise latest in matrix</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"3456" data-end=3D"3520">
<p data-start=3D"3458" data-end=3D"3520">Python: <code data-start=3D"3466" =
data-end=3D"3482">python-version</code> default / otherwise highest in matr=
ix</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start=3D"3522" data-end=3D"3553">Command extraction (practical):</p=
>
<ul data-start=3D"3554" data-end=3D"3856">
<li data-start=3D"3554" data-end=3D"3617">
<p data-start=3D"3556" data-end=3D"3617">prefer steps that run <code data-s=
tart=3D"3578" data-end=3D"3588">npm test</code>, <code data-start=3D"3590" =
data-end=3D"3601">pnpm test</code>, <code data-start=3D"3603" data-end=3D"3=
611">pytest</code>, etc.</p>
</li>
<li data-start=3D"3618" data-end=3D"3856">
<p data-start=3D"3620" data-end=3D"3856">if steps are hidden inside composi=
te actions / reusable workflows and you can=E2=80=99t extract commands conf=
idently =E2=86=92 mark =E2=80=9Cnon-inferable locally=E2=80=9D and rely on =
GitHub-only for that repo (still OK; you just can=E2=80=99t =E2=80=9Cvalida=
te locally first=E2=80=9D there).</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start=3D"3858" data-end=3D"3861">
<h2 data-start=3D"3863" data-end=3D"3898">Force-push policy (keep it sane)<=
/h2>
<ul data-start=3D"3899" data-end=3D"4099">
<li data-start=3D"3899" data-end=3D"3952">
<p data-start=3D"3901" data-end=3D"3952">Only ever force-push <strong data-=
start=3D"3922" data-end=3D"3940">stack branches</strong> (<code data-start=
=3D"3942" data-end=3D"3951">stack/*</code>)</p>
